            <formalpara>
                <title>Log pre-processing:</title>
                <para/>
            </formalpara>
            <para>Depending on the type of pre-processing, the rate at which &abbrev; collects messages can vary. Rewriting, using parsers, as well as pattern recognition processing through PatternDB have a significant impact on the message processing rate. Regular expressions have only a light impact, while facility filtering and tag filtering have virtually no impact at all.</para>
            <para>Note that in a multithreaded environment, PatternDB has a particularly large impact on performance. </para>
